            <title>[PIG-3616] TestBuiltIn.testURIwithCurlyBrace() silently fails</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3616</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This test runs against MiniCluster but takes the input from the local path.&lt;br/&gt;
The empty catch block swallows the exception (&quot;input path does not exist&quot;) thus making a false negative result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
